01:33:29.000 --> 01:33:31.000
for their fulfillment.

01:33:31.000 --> 01:33:33.000
What should others do?

01:33:33.000 --> 01:33:35.000
What should my activity be?

01:33:35.000 --> 01:33:37.000
And there are other people,

01:33:37.000 --> 01:33:41.000
who are interested in my proposal.

01:33:41.000 --> 01:33:45.000
Okay, I have already reached certain limits,

01:33:45.000 --> 01:33:49.000
I have already reached a certain position on the market.

01:33:49.000 --> 01:33:53.000
Will it shake my position?

01:33:53.000 --> 01:33:58.000
Will it make me do something again?

01:33:58.000 --> 01:34:01.000
The difference between active and passive.

01:34:01.000 --> 01:34:04.000
Someone is an activist, someone is a stabilizer.

01:34:04.000 --> 01:34:06.000
Give the activist a direction.

01:34:06.000 --> 01:34:08.000
Tell him what to do.

01:34:08.000 --> 01:34:10.000
And accordingly, it will be his motivation

01:34:10.000 --> 01:34:12.000
