01:34:12.000 --> 01:34:14.000
And the stabilizer, on the contrary.

01:34:14.000 --> 01:34:16.000
I already have this stability.

01:34:16.000 --> 01:34:20.000
How can I strengthen this stability even more?

01:34:20.000 --> 01:34:22.000
It doesn't matter.

01:34:22.000 --> 01:34:25.000
And it's not about what is good or bad,

01:34:25.000 --> 01:34:27.000
to be active or passive.

01:34:27.000 --> 01:34:32.000
People are divided by their ways of motivation in information.

01:34:32.000 --> 01:34:35.000
And if you want to get their understanding,

01:34:35.000 --> 01:34:38.000
